The SA has the same steps of the BlA and BA to select the most appropriate stack. Indeed, after the
selection of the block, bay and stack stacking rule, SA checks in the ğ¶ğ¶ğ¶ğ¶ğµğµğµğµğµğµ if such combination of rules
